Announcements
In an effort for Reese Public Schools to educate our students during the COVID-19 pandemic, RPS will be making chrome books available to student for home use in grade 6-11. While students will be able to use there own preferred device, a number of chrome books will be avalable to students that do not have their own device. If you are in need of a Chromebook, please contact Mr. Galsterer (bgalsterer@reese.k12.mi.us) or fill out the attached form at the following link https://forms.gle/Cvn1PHEKyGoPfi618
