GSRP Startup
Reese is now taking applications for preschool Great Start Readiness Program (GSRP)! This is a central intake link with our Tuscola Intermediate School District. Families interested in preschool can follow the link to apply. Your application will be submitted to an enrollment team which will review your application and the documentation you submit. There are many free and low-cost options, please apply regardless of income. If you need assistance in completing the application, please call the number included in the link.
